Package org.opends.server.protocols.ldap

Class SearchResultDoneProtocolOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.protocols.ldap.ProtocolOp
      • org.opends.server.protocols.ldap.SearchResultDoneProtocolOp
  • public class SearchResultDoneProtocolOp
extends ProtocolOp
    This class defines the structures and methods for an LDAP search result done protocol op, which is used to provide information about the result of processing a search request.
